text: Sophie Cookson (born 15 May 1990) is an English actress. She is known for playing secret agent Roxanne "Roxy" Morton / Lancelot in Kingsman: The Secret Service and its 2017 sequel The Golden Circle. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English television actors Category:English voice actors Category:English stage actors Category:People from West Sussex
